quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  23,105,"Alam takun ayatee tutlaAAalaykum fakuntum biha tukaththiboon"
  23,106,"Qaloo rabbana ghalabatAAalayna shiqwatuna wakunna qawman dalleen"
  23,107,"Rabbana akhrijna minhafa-in AAudna fa-inna thalimoon"
  23,108,"Qala ikhsaoo feeha walatukallimoon"
  23,109,"Innahu kana fareequn min AAibadeeyaqooloona rabbana amanna faghfirlana warhamna waanta khayru arrahimeen"
  23,110,"Fattakhathtumoohumsikhriyyan hatta ansawkum thikree wakuntumminhum tadhakoon"
  23,111,"Innee jazaytuhumu alyawma bima sabarooannahum humu alfa-izoon"
  23,112,"Qala kam labithtum fee al-ardiAAadada sineen"
  23,113,"Qaloo labithna yawman aw baAAdayawmin fas-ali alAAaddeen"
  23,114,"Qala in labithtum illaqaleelan law annakum kuntum taAAlamoon"
  23,115,"Afahasibtum annama khalaqnakumAAabathan waannakum ilayna la turjaAAoon"
  23,116,"FataAAala Allahualmaliku alhaqqu la ilaha illa huwarabbu alAAarshi alkareem"
  23,117,"Waman yadAAu maAAa Allahi ilahanakhara la burhana lahu bihi fa-innamahisabuhu AAinda rabbihi innahu la yuflihualkafiroon"
  23,118,"Waqul rabbi ighfir warhamwaanta khayru arrahimeen"
